Hi @jychien, I've created a PR (#3541) with the epithelium terms for the colon regions as requested. I've added terms for ascending colon epithelium, transverse colon epithelium, descending colon epithelium, and sigmoid colon epithelium. Each term has an equivalent class definition with 'intestinal epithelium' in the genus position and textual definitions following the pattern 'An epithelial layer that lines the {gut region}'.

The PR is available at: https://github.com/obophenotype/uberon/pull/3541

